# HTTPS + security (Cloudflare Pages applies these to static responses)
# Ensure "Always Use HTTPS" is ON (SSL/TLS → Edge Certificates) so HTTP upgrades before HSTS applies.

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
